(224, 1, '2014-01-27 17:21:55', '2014-01-27 17:21:55', 'And of course she was great! Got her a little bit of backyard fun in before her heartworm treatments started today. So she''ll be spending the night at the vet and I''ll be able to go get her after work tomorrow. Hopefully she does well, apparently I have to keep her from excitement and exercise for like 2 months. Which may or may not be difficult. So far she''s been a pretty chill gal. But she also wants to go run around and play games, I can tell. And 2 months of chilling may be tough haha. Especially when I personally want to go running around and playing frisbee with her too.\r\n<div class="content-img">\r\n<a href="http://localhost:8888/bunkk/media/chiguhr-01.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-223" src="http://localhost:8888/bunkk/media/chiguhr-01-300x225.jpg" alt="chiguhr-at-my-parents" width="300" height="225" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\nWe''ll have to see.\r\n\r\nI also got rid of my bed in my process to become more minimalistic and I''ve bought the indoor hanging kit from ENO to hang up my hammock as my bed. Also works great as a lounging around watch tv read a book kind of place. I approve, highly!', 'Chiguhr met my parents.', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '208-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-27 17:21:55', '2014-01-27 17:21:55', '', 208, 'http://localhost:8888/bunkk/208-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
