(9, 1, '2014-01-02 20:41:32', '2014-01-02 20:41:32', '<h4 class="title-head"><em>Ft. Worth''s premier destination for great food and craft beer.</em></h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-44 imgborder" alt="pourhouse garage exterior" src="http://localhost:8888/pourhouse/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Screen-Shot-2014-01-03-at-9.20.42-AM.png" style="width: 50%; height: auto; float: left; margin-right: 20px;" /></p>\r\nLocated on West 7th Street in Fort Worth, we have 75 craft beers on tap with an extensive collection of rare bottles and cans to complement our drafts. Chef Alfonso prepares dishes that put typical bar food to shame and our meals are delicious and affordable. We welcome all sports fans, and we show all of your favorite local teams'' games.\r\n<br>\r\nWe also have the NFL Sunday Ticket on over 45 Flat screen TV''s. On weekends, you can enjoy local, live music on our stage. Our newly remodeled space offers an open and inviting feel that includes a game room with darts, shuffleboard, pool, Golden Tee and Power Putt.', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2014-01-03 16:06:29', '2014-01-03 16:06:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/pourhouse/?page_id=9', 0, 'page', '', 0),
