(28, 1, '2013-09-10 10:05:26', '2013-09-10 10:05:26', 'So the other day I purchased bunkk.com without really knowing anything about what I would do with it. Well, for a while now I''ve been wanting to upload my .psd files online for people to download and use for their web design or whatever. So, I just decided to turn bunkk.com into something like that for myself and possibly others in the future.\r\n\r\nThe whole idea just kept growing and growing and the next thing I knew I was putting together mock ups of something that''s a lot bigger than what I had originally planned. And that''s so rad to me. I love it when my ideas just get a good footing and take off, ya''know!\r\n\r\nSo with that being said, everyone should go check out bunkk.com and see some of the updates come along while I put together an overall strategy for the website and what it will hold. But I''m thinking maybe a big community and resource center for web designers, sounds like fun huh!\r\n\r\nStay tuned and check it, yo!', 'bunkk.com', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '24-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-10 10:05:26', '2013-09-10 10:05:26', '', 24, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/24-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
